{"tid":511050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【慎入●殺狗祭新車】當街虐死黑狗灑血 迷信車主咁樣保平安？","createTime":"2017-12-27T05:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T05:52:10.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"649abde1242a6a086c31e6dc8057b9fa404309f4","tid":511050,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:52:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171227&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57628431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171227%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57628431&d=hfWUNa6%2FVpXfuI8YhkX16m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=15ceda3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171227%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57628431&h=29c204f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171227&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57628431</a><br />\n實在是離譜！湖南長沙一名購買新車的車主，昨日拿車之時，帶着一隻黑狗到場，之後當街拿着利器狂打狗頭，聲稱要「殺狗祭車保平安」。現場網民拍到的影片顯示，小狗被狂敲發出陣陣悽厲的慘叫聲，最後一命嗚呼。這名殘忍的車主拿着小狗，繞着新車，讓狗狗的血灑滿地上，最後這名車主更稱「輪胎上也灑點」，這樣才能保平安。<br />\n<br />\n網民看過片段，齊聲咀咒這名殘忍的車主，並說：「這車注定車禍沾上他們全家的血！」「車主馬上要有血光之災，估計要車毀人亡！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/27/135202_9ca9a20e32925fac5bf82a402bf61530.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F27%2F135202_9ca9a20e32925fac5bf82a402bf61530.jpeg&h=3fd0e7d5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}